column1: All data are in 000 metric tonnes of nutrients
column2: Went to https://www.ifastat.org/databases/plant-nutrition then selected all countries, the years from 1986 to 2019, then for 'Which products' the 'Grant Total N', 'Grand Total P2O5' and 'Grand Total K20' were chosen. In addition the display options for 'Total N+P2O5+K2O' was selected. For Activities 'Consumption' was chosen. Then 'Show data' was pressed, and then once the data were displayed 'Download results' was pressed. The xlsx file had the second row deleted as well as the bottom rows that had extraneous information (on IFA copyright and when the data were downloaded). This was saved as a csv file.
